Player Function:

--(Position)--

You can't just use workspace:GetDescendants({player}) , all you can use is Mineblox Function to get Player Position.

So how? you can use Player.Position(player) , allowing your plugin to get The Specificed Player Position.

Get the specificed Player Position and show Message of Player Position:

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Arugments.Import(player)
Arugments.Import(SendMessage)
local PlayerPosition = Player.Position(player)

SendMessage:Private("Superproinf Position: "..PlayerPosition.." (XYZ)", Superproinf123) {Message, SendTo}
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
